article.headline: California Riverside 88, Vanguard 63
article.story: RIVERSIDE, Calif. (AP) -- Larry Cunningham had a game-high 19 points and 11 rebounds in UC Riverside's 88-63 rout over Vanguard Wednesday night. Benoit Bekono added a career-high 18 points for UC Riverside (2-2). Justin Bell's 4-of-7 shooting from long range helped Riverside build a 44-37 halftime lead. In the second half, Riverside outscored Vanguard 44-26, including a 17-4 run in the last seven minutes. The Lions (1-3) were led by Dennis Heenan with 15 points on 6-of-12 shooting, including three 3-pointers. Miguel Rosales and Kevin Dalafu added 13 points apiece for Vanguard.
